														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2067040">
									

<p>What's with all the &quot;they&quot; or &quot;them&quot;? I understand English is lacking in gender-neutral pronouns, but is &quot;it&quot; really so inappropriate here? Especially in a piece that deals so much with an actual collectively designated group.</p>

