<p>I can't in good conscience upvote this, because of the last line:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Certainly, it would go yet further towards explaining the Jailors' general hatred of knowledge and scientific inquiry.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>That just seems like a poorly-done jab at the Foundation. I get that the SH isn't exactly on the best terms with them, but even they have to admit that the Foundation is at least <em>trying</em> to be scientifically inquisitive. The rest of it is good, but that last line just ruins it for me.</p>
<p>Neutral vote.</p>

