														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2275278">
									

<p>I was reminded that I needed to update this article, and so I have.</p>
<p>Major changes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Explained the name &quot;Summer's Exile&quot; (formerly only explained in what amounted to an Easter egg). Explained what &quot;Summer&quot; might mean.</li>
<li>Made the mythological reference to Sisyphus more explicit (the implication wasn't really coming across to readers).</li>
<li>Added more possibilities with the Foundation which weren't really implied even though they were supposed to be.</li>
<li>A few more elements made more explicit.</li>
<li>Made a bunch of minor edits for clarity &amp; readability. Notably, I changed the biggest Jailor jab to a footnote since people found it distracting.</li>
</ul>
<p>I haven't messed with the pronouns. I still might change to 'she' if people think that reads better, given that the Exile is not human.</p>

							</div>

								
